title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 18 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 18 2022
description:
Elon Musk’s fight for freedom on socials is a battle for the ages. Twitter co-founder and former CEO Jack Dorsey lashes out at "poison pill," as Elon Musk tries to buy company. Musk owes a tremendous amount in U.S. taxes after wrapping up his Tesla stock sales. CIA has known Trump-Russia collusion data not "technically plausible" since 2017, Durham says. Biden's White House Covid Response Coordinator Ashish Jha: "The pandemic is not over." Only 15 more days of mask mandates. Good news: Florida judge voids U.S. mask mandate for planes, other travel. The madness continues: iPhone update adds 'pregnant man' emoji.
